{
  "stem": "23278.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the old man, the old father Oppenheimer, the old grandfather-- he looked like a white rabbit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say white rabbit because he had white hair, and he always had a problem with his eyes that were red.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a little, tiny man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had to go shopping in the morning for food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had his yellow star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we used to hold on together so his yellow star wouldn't show.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only problem it is that his coupons had a big J on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So by the fact that he had a big J, he couldn't go to a store before 11:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stood in line at 5:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By the time 11:00 came, it was nothing left except a few onions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the grocer could not accept those tickets because of the J.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If I took his tickets, it wouldn't be accepted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the grocery man was a nice man, so we managed to smuggle a few things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then two people I knew at my church, we got false coupon, without the J, so they could at least feed themselves, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had to buy flour at the black market, sugar at the black market, to make their cookies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they had to need potatoes and other things and meat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you see, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then they left Dijon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they went in the Alps near Aix-les-Bains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, but they sent me a note--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they were able to get out because--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time, it was where the demarcation line-- and it was after Pearl Harbor, and the Germans occupied all of France, so you could rarely travel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't travel with much, a few-- a few trunks.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
